In your GitHub repo root, create this path:
api/contact.js
So the structure is:
WebScalePH/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ index.html
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ assets/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ api/
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ contact.js   ‚Üê THIS FILE
