# PART 1 ‚Äî CREATE `/api/contact.js` IN GITHUB (BACKEND)

## STEP 1: Open your GitHub repository

1. Go to **GitHub**
2. Open your repo:
   üëâ `georgebakerofficial-wq / WebScalePH`
3. You should see the file list (`index.html`, assets, etc.)

